ArtyTorrent Pack 93-House Drum Loops 140-149bpm-WAV samples
-----------------------------------------------------------

A small pack of tribal and progressive house drum loops for use in electronic music productions ranging from 140-149 bpm.

Torrent contains 3 RAR files with 70 loops
------------------------------------------
Housey 140 (11 loops)
Misc House 140-149 (49)
Pumpin 145 (10)

Samples are from a variety of sources including CDs by EastWest and Sony/Sonic Foundry, and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.
